				<h1 class="shead-style text-center">CHHATISGARH</h1>
				<p>For most part of the history this state was forgotten or not recognized for various reasons. But now it is a colorful and vibrant state with profound wildlife and modernization. A land gifted with rare wildlife, beautifully carved monuments, caves, palaces, hills and plateaus, it is truly a land of surprises. Many of the scriptures, palaces, temples, palaces, cave paintings date back to hundreds of years. This explains the history and culture it had for a long time.
        </p><p>Being a place of dense woodlands and housing variety of wildlife some which are rare throughout the world, it boasts a pride about its nature. Many of the waterfalls which fall through various mountains are also one of the most visited places in the state. A state indescribable in its own way definitely deserves your visit.
        </p>
